OL,3,CFour students jailed after knife and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat brawl
OL,6,FFour men who used knives and a
OL,7,Fbaseball bat in a fight in Leicester
OL,8,Fcity centre have been jailed after
OL,9,Fthey left an 18-year-old hospitalised
OL,10,Fwith stab injuries.
OL,12,FAll four were students at De Montfort
OL,13,FUniversity in Leicester at the time of
OL,14,Fthe incident and were sentenced at the
OL,15,Fconclusion of a six-week trial.
OL,17,FThe fight broke out at around 3am on 4
OL,18,FNovember 2021, when the four men had a
OL,19,Fverbal altercation with another group,
OL,20,Fwhich then led to a large fight.
