OL,3,CFour students jailed after knife and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat brawl
OL,6,FOne of the men, 21-year-old Destiny
OL,7,FOjo was seen with a baseball bat, and
OL,8,F21-year-old Ridwanulahi Raheem was
OL,9,Flater seen carrying a large knife.
OL,11,F21-year-old Habib Lawal was seen
OL,12,Fcarrying what was believed to be a
OL,13,Fknife.
OL,15,FA man from the other group was thrown
OL,16,Fto the ground and stabbed four times.
OL,17,FHe was taken to hospital and was later
OL,18,Fdischarged.
