OL,3,CFour students jailed after knife and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat brawl
OL,6,FLeicestershire Police Detective
OL,7,FConstable Sean Downey said: "This
OL,8,Fincident highlights the serious danger
OL,9,Fof violent disorder.
OL,11,F"It is extremely fortunate that
OL,12,Ffurther injury was not caused to the
OL,13,Fpeople involved or to other members of
OL,14,Fthe public who witnessed the incident.
OL,16,F"This could have been a very different
OL,17,Finvestigation.
