OL,6,F"Following the disorder, a full
OL,7,Finvestigation took place with suspects
OL,8,Fbeing identified at different stages
OL,9,Fthrough CCTV enquiries, phone work and
OL,10,Fpublic appeals.
OL,12,F"Thank you to everyone who has
OL,13,Fassisted us throughout this
OL,14,Finvestigation and provided
OL,15,Finformation. As a force, our priority
OL,16,Fis to keep the public safe.
OL,18,F"We will not tolerate violent disorder
OL,19,Fin our communities and will take
OL,20,Faction against those who are
OL,21,Fresponsible for it."
